== Sequels ==
Sony stated that they may film the sequel, ''[[The Girl Who Played with Fire]]'', back-to-back with the third installment, ''[[The Girl Who Kicked the Hornets' Nest]]'', for a late 2013 release. Mara and Craig are contracted for the remaining films.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/girl-played-fire-track/ |title=The Girl Who Played with Fire Still On Track |publisher=WeGotThisCovered.com |date=2012-01-03 |accessdate=2012-03-23}}</ref> It is unclear whether Fincher will return to direct the sequels. At the [[84th Academy Awards]], Mara stated that filming would begin in the autumn.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/films.php?id=85606/ |title=The Girl Who Played with Fire |publisher=Comingsoon.net |date= |accessdate=2012-03-23}}</ref>

